# <type>(<scope>): <subject>
#
# Subject: imperative mood, lowercase, no period, max 72 chars.
# Types:   feat | fix | refactor | perf | test | docs | build | ci | chore | style
# Scopes:  shm | runtime | backend | qml | codegen | ci | docs
#
# Examples:
#   feat(shm): add CRC32 checksum to DisplayDataShm
#   fix(backend): emit displayHealth on heartbeat timeout
#   refactor(runtime): extract alarm policy to pure function
#   test(shm): cover magic + version + CRC fault injection
#   ci: split ut-only job from full build job
#
# Body (optional, wrap at 72):
#   - why, not what (the diff shows what)
#   - link issue / REQ id (Refs: REQ-SYS-005)
#
# Footer:
#   Refs: REQ-XXX-NNN
#   Breaking-Change: describe migration

